					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sure, it's real easy.  Have something like this:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda #0 ;&#40;select bank number here&#41;<br />tax<br />sta bankpages,x<br /><br />bankpages: .byte 0,1,2,3<br /></div>
<br />
<br />Because of bus conflicts, you have to write a value to ROM only where that same value is already so it'll work on a real cart.  The bankpages label and indexed write to it takes care of that.</div>

