						<div class="postbody">The rom should be 64kB because mapper 3 is always 32kB PRG + 32kB CHR.
<br />
<br />The bankpages label needs to be in ROM, $0000 would be RAM.  Put it anywhere between $8000 to $FFFF and see if that helps.</div>

